Description: Eborhood.com is a marketplace that allows people and businesses to trade goods and services locally.
Full Description: Eborhood.com is a marketplace that allows people and businesses to trade goods and services locally.   Eborhood enables buying, selling and bartering using a drag-and-drop platform that seamlessly allows goods and services to be exchanged.  This e-commerce platform is free of charge and only accepts tips of any amount designated by its users.  Eborhood focuses on building a zero-crime environment online. So, safety is Eborhood's priority -- members have a variety of options to verify one's identity using data available publicly, socially and via private channels.  This helps prevent anonymous criminals to run rampant on the Eborhood network.  In order to ensure a safe transactional experience, Eborhood pinpoints a public meeting spot equidistant between buyers and sellers.  This helps facilitate the exchange of items in a safe manner since criminals are deterred from committing crimes in public places. Eborhood can be used to swap TVs for laptops, baseball cards for video games, textbooks for maid service or anything else imaginable.
